summary: An ordinance providing for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of Gilman Avenue from the west margin of 11th Avenue West, to a point 50 feet more or less, Northwest therefrom; providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor; and providing that the cost of said improvement shall be paid by special assessment upon the property specially benefited in the manner provided by law.
